Hi,
      This patch displays x86 flags in /proc/cpuflags :
e.g.
flag1   :yes
flag2   :no
flagx   :yes
...
PS:It works on x86 evaluating first processor flags (generic?).
PS2:Why ? current cpuinfo displays all _available_ flags only and in queue
mode.
Regards,
FabF
